This project allows user to take a screenshot of a webpage which links WEKU blockchain and uses Selerium webdriver.

Copywight - Grace C.

HOW TO RUN?

WEB-part
cd factom-db
npm run start

REST-part
cd www/restapi
node app.js


For Chinese font, I had it solved by the following steps:
sudo apt-get install language-pack-zh-hans
sudo apt-get install ttf-arphic-uming
sudo apt-get install ttf-dejavu ttf-wqy-microhei
sudo fc-cache -f -v
OS is Ubuntu 12.04 LTS


# Install Chrome and ChromeDriver
sudo apt-get install libxss1 libappindicator1 libindicator7
wget https://dl.google.com/linux/direct/google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb
sudo apt install ./google-chrome*.deb

downlad chrom driver from Selenium



echo "# webshot" >> README.md
git init
git add README.md
git commit -m "first commit"
git remote add origin https://github.com/gracechen4/webshot.git
git push -u origin master
